reviews.text:
Nice atmosphere. Plenty of space. Lovely tall flat white from the reserve part. It cost $48. 

But, I find it annoying you can't slouch in the chairs and get really comfortable, although they look really comfortable. I've tried different ones and about 3 different seats all had this same feeling.

Cool space in a very cool location
Selection is almost the same as per every Starbucks... But they also have the reserve selection

What can I say...I'm a coffee addict. Starbucks is like the convenient store round every corner of the streets. I JUST NEED THE CAFFEINE.  They might not have the best quality n taste, but sure they have the not too bad qualities of what you need to feed on...
🤣🤣🤣Sounds like a meth store. LOL
Quiet, clean and spacious one but no reserve/nitro yet as of this post
Nice coffee
